menguasai langit di atas Selat.

638
00:52:43,076 --> 00:52:46,580
Kemenangan tidak
datang tanpa pengorbanan.

639
00:52:48,790 --> 00:52:50,000
Evelyn.

640
00:52:50,083 --> 00:52:51,501
Danny.

