00:59:35,738 --> 00:59:38,366
- Anthony, tekan nomor enam.
- Baiklah.

744
00:59:38,449 --> 00:59:41,703
- Gooz, ketuk nomor tiga.
- Baiklah.

745
00:59:41,786 --> 00:59:44,789
Hai. Kami mendapat pengunjung.

