mati. Bawa dia...

1316
02:01:45,756 --> 02:01:47,425
Tuhan.

1317
02:01:48,968 --> 02:01:52,138
Apakah Anda yakin, Ev? Bisakah
Anda memeriksanya sekali lagi?

